<div id="content" class="content wikipage" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<p id="l1">
A type of <a title="Font" href="Font">font</a> using a system which is an alternative to the <a title="Unit System" href="Unit_System">unit system</a>. A unitized font utilizes an <a title="Escapement" href="Escapement">escapement</a> value assigned to each character appropriate to a particular <a title="Typeface" href="Typeface">typeface</a>, allowing greater character fit than is possible under the unit system. 
</p>
